trans-unit.target: Contém um conjunto de <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReference"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceReferenceCollection object contains a <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference> object for each Web service that is registered in an AJAX-enabled ASP.NET page.
trans-unit.target: O objeto de ServiceReferenceCollection contém um <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>objeto para cada serviço Web que está registado numa página ASP.NET AJAX-ativado.</xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>

trans-unit.source: Web services can be defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control or in an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control.
trans-unit.target: Serviços Web podem ser definidos no <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>controlo ou um associados <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy>controlo.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: You can add Web services to the ServiceReferenceCollection object declaratively by adding one or more `<asp:ServiceReference>` elements to a `<Services>` element inside the `<asp:ScriptManager>` element on the page, as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Pode adicionar serviços Web para o objeto de ServiceReferenceCollection forma declarativa adicionando um ou mais `<asp:ServiceReference>` elementos um `<Services>` elemento dentro do `<asp:ScriptManager>` elemento na página, conforme mostrado no exemplo seguinte.

trans-unit.source: ``` <asp:ScriptManager ID="SM1" runat="server"> <Services> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service1.asmx" /> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service2.asmx" /> </Services> </asp:ScriptManager> ``` You can also programmatically add a <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A> collection by using the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A> method of the ServiceReferenceCollection class.
trans-unit.target: ``` <asp:ScriptManager ID="SM1" runat="server"> <Services> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service1.asmx" /> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service2.asmx" /> </Services> </asp:ScriptManager> ```Através de programação também pode adicionar um <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>objeto à <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A>coleção utilizando o <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A>método de classe ServiceReferenceCollection.</xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>

trans-unit.source: Web services are registered with the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control during the page's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender> life cycle stage.
trans-unit.target: Serviços Web estão registados com o <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>controlo durante a página <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender>fase do ciclo de vida.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReferenceCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReferenceCollection"> </xref> classe.
